# xlog whitepaper — only the rendered PDF and the directory README are tracked
# on the default branch. LaTeX source, build artifacts, figure sources, and
# figure build outputs are all excluded from the GitHub-visible tree.
#
# Full source history remains available on the `audit/v0.5.0-prerelease` branch
# (see README.md). If you need to rebuild or modify the whitepaper, check out
# that branch, which has the complete LaTeX pipeline.

# LaTeX source
*.tex
*.sty
*.bib
latexmkrc
Makefile

# Mermaid figure sources + rendered figures
figures/*.mmd
figures/*.pdf

# LaTeX build artifacts
*.aux
*.bbl
*.bcf
*.blg
*.fdb_latexmk
*.fls
*.log
*.out
*.run.xml
*.synctex.gz
*.toc
*.lof
*.lot
*.nav
*.snm
*.vrb
